Hi Lily,

Thanks for sharing the document.

Here is a brief summary of the content:
- It is a feedback note following the first discussion meeting of our Book Club.
- The note appreciates participants' insights on "The Great Gatsby."
- It announces that the next book for the Book Club meeting will be "The Old Man and the Sea."
- It asks readers to view an online resource at www.bookclub.com.

Best regards,
Emma
